---
title: Sweet Soy-Glazed Chicken & Noodle Bar One recipe–endless ways to enjoy!
description: Introducing our chef-curated “perfect plates,” where everyone builds their own meal. This one stars sweet ’n’ spicy soy-glazed dark meat chicken with springy ramen noodles, roasted broccoli, and a lineup of tantalizing toppers: tangy cucumber pickles, crispy fried onions, crunchy peanuts, and fresh scallions. If you ordered extras, you can add green beans or jasmine rice too!

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66e876a72d58b223b75b9a84-f1efdb32.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/66eb4e3b0f7b9c1397d66aac-en-US.pdf
